---
layout: default
meta_title: Blog
meta_description: Blog page description
body_class: blog
title: The Solarflux Blog
---

<main>
  <section class="article-hero">
    <h1>Insights</h1>
    <img src="/images/blog/blog-hero.png" alt="">
  </section>

  <section class="max-w-6xl px-4 mx-auto mt-24 mb-16 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <h2 class="mb-6 text-3xl font-bold text-center text-gray-900">All About Solar</h2>
    <p class="text-xl font-light text-center text-gray-600">Introduction to the blog text. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Mi est massa varius vulputate viverra senectus eleifend. Ultricies integer elementum non eget at etiam imperdiet odio vel.</p>
  </section>
  
  <section class="max-w-6xl px-4 mx-auto mt-24 mb-16" aria-label="Blogs">

    <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-6 posts">

      {% for post in collections.blog %}

      <article class="flex-1 overflow-hidden bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg article-card">

        <a class="relative block overflow-hidden featured-image-link" href="{{ post.url }}">

          <figure>
            <img data-lazy="{{ post.data.featured_image }}" class="block">
          </figure>

        </a>

        <div class="px-4 py-6">

          <div class="{{ post.data.category | categoryStyle()}}">
            <a href="/blog/{{ post.data.category | lower }}/" class="px-2 py-1 text-sm no-underline rounded-full">{{ post.data.category }}</a>
          </div>

          <h2 class="mt-3 mb-2 text-xl">
            <a class="block text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 hover:text-gray-600" href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a>
          </h2>

          <div class="mb-4 text-sm text-gray-600 md:flex">
            <svg class="w-4 mr-2" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewbox="0 0 24 24">
                <defs>
                    <style>
                        .a {
                            fill: none;
                            stroke: currentColor;
                            stroke-linecap: round;
                            stroke-linejoin: round;
                            stroke-width: 1.5px;
                        }
                    </style>
                </defs>
                <rect width="22.5" height="19.5" x=".752" y="3.75" class="a" rx="1.5" ry="1.5"/>
                <path d="M.752 9.75h22.5M6.752 6V.75M17.252 6V.75" class="a"/>
            </svg>
            <time datetime="{{ post.date }}">
              {{ post.date | dateDisplay }}
            </time>

          </div>

          <div>
          <div class="text-base text-gray-600">
            {{ post.templateContent | renderExcerpt(80)}}
          </div>

        </div>

      </article>

      {% endfor %}

    </div>

  </section>
  <!-- Contact Form -->
  <section>
    {% include 'components/form.njk' %}
  </section>
</main>